</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Plewral suwuklygy &ouml;wrenmek&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>.&nbsp;<b>Pleura&nbsp;</b>&ouml;&yacute;keni&#328;
