almagy boz&yacute;ar.&nbsp;<b>PH&nbsp;</b>derejesini&nbsp;<b>,&nbsp;</b>belogy&#328;,
&ouml;&yacute;j&uuml;kleri&#328; bardygyny, laktat dehidrojenazy&#328; (LDH)
